attention is} 21... Qa7 $5 22. Qg3 {[%cal Oc3a4] next Nc3-a4! is good for
White.} Bd7 $1 {Black shouldn't be too greedy. Leaving the danger zone is
preferable.} 23. Rxd6 {Nc3-a4 would now be deadly.} O-O-O $1 24. Qg7 Kb8 {
after ...Bc8 Black should be able to liquidate into an acceptable endgame.})
22. Qg8+ Rf8 23. Qg1 Rf7 24. Qg8+ {GM YU, Yangyi decides to call it a day.} ({
It was possible to maintain the tension by means of} 24. Bc4 Rg7 25. Qb6 Qc7 {
White hardly has anything special.} 26. Qe3 Bb7 {[%cal Od6d5]} 27. Be6 $44 {
White has full compensation, but hardly more.}) 24... Rf8 25. Qg1 {Not much
