{E20: Nimzo-Indian: 4 g3 and 4 f3} 1. d4 Nf6 2. c4 e6 3. Nc3 Bb4 4. f3 d5 5. a3
Be7 6. e4 dxe4 7. fxe4 {e4-e5 would now be deadly. 7.a4 gains popularity. 7.a4
wird beliebter.} c5 8. d5 {has lost popularity (8.a4). verliert an Beliebtheit
(8.a4).} exd5 $146 {White has an edge.} 9. exd5 O-O 10. Be2 a6 11. Nf3 h6 12.
O-O Bd6 {Prevents Bc1-f4} 13. h3 (13. Nh4 Re8 14. Nf5 Bxf5 15. Rxf5 Be5 16.
