bxc4 (19... Nh5 {feels hotter.} 20. gxh6 Bf4 21. Rg2 Bxc1 22. Rxc1 Qf6) 20.
bxc4 {[#]} Bxh3 {[%eval -34,19] This pair of bishops is nice.} (20... Nh5 $1
$17 {[%eval -97,23]} 21. Rg2 Nf4 (21... Bxh3 22. gxh6 Bxg2 23. Ng5 $15) 22.
