Kg1 Rh8 46. Kf1 Rhd8) 44. Qe5 Rd7 45. Qxf4+ Ke8 $11 46. Kg1 Rg8+ 47. Kf2 Rg2+
48. Ke3 Rgd2 49. Qe5 R7d3+ 50. Kf4 Kf7 51. Qxa5 b3 52. Qc7+ (52. Qh5+) 52...
Rd7 53. Qb6 b2 $1 54. Ke5 (54. Kg3 Rg2+ 55. Kxh3 Rdd2) (54. c5 $132 {With a
