E Aktobe 2022, and White has only a nominal space advantage. However, much
later, he was able to profit from his advanced h-pawn to win in the endgame.})
17. Bg5 Qh5 18. e5 $146 (18. Rxc8 Rxc8 19. g4 Qh3 20. Rf2 Nc4 21. Bxc4 Rxc4 22.
