15. Nxd3) 14... exf5 {Amongst all the options this is by far the best one due
to a few factors: 1. Trading off the light squared bishops only helped white.
2. N on d5 is a monster and Nc6-e7 is impossible as the bishop on f6 is
vulnerable 3. White's N in clearly superior to Black's B Unter allen Optionen
ist dies die mit Abstand beste, und zwar aufgrund mehrerer Faktoren: 1. Der
