40. Rd3+ Ke2 41. Nd4+ {1-0 Kosteniuk-Koneru, Saint Louis 2023}) 17. Ng3 Bg6 18.
h4 h6 $11) (15. Bg3 {Esipenko-Yakubboev, Almaty 2022} Rhe8 $11) 15... Kxc7 (
15... Bxe4 16. Bxb6 axb6 17. Rxe4 $14 {gives White a riskfree edge in
Nguyen-Ganguly, Saint Louis 2022}) 16. Nxc5 Rae8 $1 {Very accurate. Once Black
captures on c2 the black king may be evacuated to b8.} (16... Rhe8 $2 17. Be6
$1 $16) 17. Be6 (17. Ne6+ Bxe6 18. Bxe6 Kd6 $11) 17... Bxc2 18. Rac1 Bg6 $1 19.
