(18. Nh3 {doesn't feel right (Knights on the rim are dim and all that!)
However after} a5 19. Qd2 f4 (19... Kh7 {is less committal}) 20. Bc5 Rb8 {
(teeing up ...e4)} 21. b3 {possibly Black should take it anyway before it
drops back to f2 and into e4. Instead} Qf6 ({So} 21... Bxh3 22. Rxh3 ({Actually
} 22. gxh3 $5 {is probably the better recapture with} Kh7 23. Bxd5 cxd5 24.
