) 13. Kb1 (13. Bxf5+ $5 gxf5 14. Qe3 {is given as unclear by Gawain. Black
looks fine after} e5 $1 $11) 13... d4 14. Nb5 Qxd2 15. Rxd2 Bg4 16. Nbxd4 {
