(2581) chess. com INT 2021} 13. Nxe4 $1 $16 {leaves Black in trouble.}) 12. Kb1
d5 (12... exf4 13. Nb5 d5 14. Nxf4 Ng8 $1 {This move could prove difficult to
find OTB.} (14... Nh5 $6 15. Qxd5 Bxf4 16. Qxe4+ Qe7 17. Qa4 {gives White a
