Qc2 Bb7 13. O-O-O Nc5 $11 {0-1 (43) Sevian,S (2660)-Robson,R (2673) Lichess.
org INT 2020}) 9... Nxf3+ 10. Bxf3 Nd7 {This is the main move which contains
