g6 5. Nf3 (5. f4 Bg7 6. Bb5+ Nfd7 7. a4 Na6 8. Nf3 Nc7 9. Bd3 O-O 10. O-O e6
11. dxe6 fxe6 12. f5 Ne5 13. fxg6 hxg6 14. Be3 Bd7 15. Nxe5 Rxf1+ 16. Bxf1 Bxe5
17. Qg4 Qf6 18. Bc4 Rf8 19. Rd1 Rf7 {Leisebein,P (1200)-Grott,P (1200) SE014
www.desc-online.de 2000 ½-½}) 5... Bg7 6. Be2 (6. Bc4 O-O 7. O-O Nbd7 8. Bf4
