28. Bf1 Qc1 29. Qh7+ Kf8 30. Rhf3 Rd7 31. Rd3 Nxe5 32. Rxf7+ Nxf7 33. Rxd7 Qg5+
34. Kh1 Rf6 35. Bc4 Qc1+ {Zhang,P (2562)-Ni,H (2390) Perenyi Memorial 2000 (7)
