Nd7 13. Be2 Rb8 14. Bh6 b5 15. axb5 axb5 16. Bxg7 Kxg7 17. b4 {Chapter 5 -
Egoism-Speelman vs. Hartston}) 3. Bf4 e6 4. Nb5 Na6 5. e3 Be7 6. Nf3 O-O 7. h4
c5 8. c3 {White has an edge.} (8. a4 Bd7 9. Ne5 Nb4 10. g4 a6 11. Nc3 cxd4 12.
exd4 Rc8 13. f3 Be8 14. Bd3 Nd7 15. g5 Nxe5 16. Bxe5) 8... Bd7 9. a4 Ne4 {
[%eval 82,18]} (9... c4 10. b3 Qa5 11. bxc4 Bxb5 12. axb5 Qxc3+ 13. Nd2 Nb4 14.
Rc1 Nd3+ 15. Bxd3 Qxd3 16. Qe2 dxc4 17. Rxc4 Qa3 18. O-O Rfc8 19. e4 a5) (9...
Bxb5 $11 {[%eval 26,22]} 10. axb5 (10. Bxb5 c4 $15) 10... Nc7) 10. h5 {[%eval
27,20]} (10. Bd3 $1 $16 {[%eval 82,18]}) 10... h6 {[%eval 72,17] is cutting
edge theory. ist die Avantgarde der Theorie.} (10... c4 $1 $11 {[%eval 27,20]})
11. Ne5 {[%eval 13,19]} (11. Bd3 $16 {[%eval 72,17]}) 11... Nb8 {[%eval 51,18]}
(11... cxd4 $11 {[%eval 13,19] deserves consideration.} 12. exd4 Bxb5 13. Bxb5
(13. axb5 Nb8 $16) 13... Nb8) 12. Bd3 $1 $14 a6 13. Na3 {[%eval 8,20] White is
more active.} ({White should play} 13. Bxe4 $14 {[%eval 68,23]} dxe4 14. Na3)
13... Nc6 {[%eval 67,21]} ({Black should try} 13... Ng5 $11 {[%eval 8,20]}) 14.
Bxe4 {[%eval 0,23]} dxe4 {[%eval 67,19]} ({Better is} 14... Nxe5 $11 {[%eval 0,
23]} 15. Bb1 Nc6) 15. Nxd7 $1 Qxd7 16. dxc5 (16. Nc4) 16... Rfd8 17. Qxd7 Rxd7
18. Ke2 {Strongly threatening Na3-c4.} e5 {[%eval 157,24]} (18... Bxc5 $14 {
[%eval 50,22]} 19. Nc4 Ne7) 19. Bg3 $16 Bxc5 20. Nc4 Re8 21. b4 Bf8 {[#]} 22.
