..Nc6-e5+.} 45. Kd5 Ne7+ 46. Kc4 $2 {[%eval -691,24]} (46. Kd6 $11 {[%eval -13,
21]}) 46... Kg5 $19 47. Nxa4 Kxg4 48. e4 Kxh5 {aiming for ...Kh5-g4.} 49. Kc5
